âœ… Uses IAM role assumption instead of AWS profiles â†’ More secure.
âœ… Works across multiple AWS accounts & regions.
âœ… Asks for confirmation before deletion â†’ Prevents accidental deletion.
âœ… Only deletes unassociated route tables â†’ No risk to active resources.
âœ… Highlights dummy account IDs & roles in red for easy replacement.

